citeinfo.origin: USDA Forest Service, Tahoe National Forest
citeinfo.title: SurfaceOwnership

descript.abstract: Data taken from the U. S. Forest Service ALP dataset. This data provides details of the surface ownership of all land within the Tahoe National Forest Boundary.
descript.purpose: As part of a developing digital data base covering all areas of Forest Service interest to support and provide information for the management of Forest Service resource programs.
descript.supplinf: There is a relationship class, Ownership, which can be joined with this Feature Class table. With that join, it is possible to query for the names and locations of the 20 major land owners inside the Tahos National Forest.
